<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
	<table with="100%" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="2">
	<tr>
		<td><a href="http://www.cloudspokes.com"><img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/cs-public/email_images/cloudspokes-logo.png" width="75"></a></td>
		<td><h2><%= @challenge.name %></h2></td>
	</tr>
	</table>
  <p><%= @membername %>,</p>

  <% if @challenge.submissions.to_i > 0 %>

		<p>The status of this challenge has been changed to "Review" and scorecards for all reviewers have been generated.</p>

		<p>Number of submissions: <%= @challenge.submissions.to_i %><br/>
		Number of reviewers: <%= @challenge.number_of_reviewers.to_i %><br/>
		<% if @challenge.community_judging %>
			Scorecards are due: <%= Date.parse(@challenge.review_date).strftime("%m/%d/%Y") %><br/>
		<% end %>			
		Winners to be announced: <%= Date.parse(@challenge.winner_announced).strftime("%m/%d/%Y") %></p>

		<p>You can view and download all files that were submitted <a href="http://www.cloudspokes.com/challenges/<%= @challenge.challenge_id %>/all_submissions">from here</a>. Reviewers will find their scorecards for the submissions to be scored on their <a href="http://www.cloudspokes.com/account/outstanding_reviews">Outstanding Reviews page</a>.</p>

	<% else %>
		<p>The status of this challenge has been changed to "Review", however there were no submissions for this challenge.</p>
	<% end %>

	<p>If you need help or have questions, please contact support@cloudspokes.com.</p>

	<p>Regards,<br/>
	The CloudSpokes Team<br/>
	// Let's build it</p>
		
  <h3 style="padding-top:25px">Follow Us!</h3>
	<table cellpadding="2" cellspacing="2">
	<tr>
		<td><a href="http://www.github.com/cloudspokes"><img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/cs-public/email_images/github_64.png"></a></td>
		<td><a href="http://www.twitter.com/cloudspokes"><img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/cs-public/email_images/twitter_64.png"></a></td>
		<td><a href="http://www.facebook.com/cloudspokes"><img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/cs-public/email_images/facebook_64.png"></a></td>
		<td><a href="http://www.youtube.com/cloudspokescommunity"><img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/cs-public/email_images/youtube_icon.png" width="59" style="padding-left:5px;padding-top:3px"></a></td>
		<td><a href="http://blog.cloudspokes.com"><img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/cs-public/email_images/blogicon.png" width="55" style="padding-left:10px;padding-top:4px"></a></td>
		<td><a href="http://www.cloudspokes.com/challenges/feed"><img src="https://s3.amazonaws.com/cs-public/email_images/rss_icon.png" width="57" style="padding-left:10px;padding-top:3px"></a></td>
	</tr>
	</table>

	<p><a href="http://www.cloudspokes.com">http://www.cloudspokes.com</a></p>

  </body>
</html>